snippet.title: Place of Decay | Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
WISHLIST ON STEAM!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3215270/Place_of_Decay/

Follow us on Twitter/X:
https://x.com/GrayBoxGames


Trapped inside a distorted and corrupted game project you navigate through a chaotic project on the brink of collapse. Your goal is to unravel the mystery of what led to the project's downfall and the reasons behind the developer's sudden abandonment. Leverage the power of the Code Cannon to transcend the confines of this twisted reality and forge a path to freedom.
